item.title: How do i delete a .bat file!
item.dc:creator: @Zach1188 Zach1188
item.description:
@Zach1188 wrote:

Turn off your computer, then turn it back on. IMMIDIATELY after pressing the power button to turn it on, keep tapping F8 until a menu comes up, and choose “Safe Mode”. Now, log into the admin account, and delete the .bat file.
